{"tid":1907280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"埃及世界文化遺產被影射中國國旗","createTime":"2020-03-02T13:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T14:02:27.000Z","uid":250888,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe178afbe5473f687e0f3487174997f78d87a68","tid":1907280,"uid":250888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.chinaarabcf.org/chn/zagx/zajw/W020200302404669959226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinaarabcf.org%2Fchn%2Fzagx%2Fzajw%2FW020200302404669959226.jpg&h=521deb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.chinaarabcf.org/chn/zagx/zajw/W020200302404669964417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinaarabcf.org%2Fchn%2Fzagx%2Fzajw%2FW020200302404669964417.jpg&h=162e3867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.chinaarabcf.org/chn/zagx/zajw/W020200302404669967868.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinaarabcf.org%2Fchn%2Fzagx%2Fzajw%2FW020200302404669967868.jpg&h=28b1c18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼杜拜同澳門之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ac89b0a674d13a059f001dca5c0dd2d82d086e","tid":1907280,"uid":250888,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:26:41.000Z","msg":"當地時間3月1日晚7點30分，埃及衛生與人口部長哈萊根據塞西總統指示，作為總統特使訪華，在哈萊起程訪華的同時，埃及三大世界文化遺產開羅薩拉丁城堡、盧克索卡爾納克神廟、阿斯旺菲萊神廟通過燈光秀的方式打出鮮豔的五星紅旗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哈萊部長向專程前來送行的中國駐埃及大使廖力強表示，她此次根據塞西總統的指示訪華，以及薩拉丁城堡、盧克索神廟、菲萊神廟同時打出中國國旗，意在向正在抗擊新冠肺炎疫情的中國政府和人民表示支持，向世界展示，在抗擊疫情這場沒有硝煙的戰爭中，埃及人民與中國人民堅定站在一起。"},{"pid":"fbe2267ad42d443019f109408fc20711fec025a7","tid":1907280,"uid":66546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:27:25.000Z","msg":"痂撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88184614252bb4049e91467e18199c6f9f6b3b58","tid":1907280,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"喜迎中國肺炎"},{"pid":"61fd90d8c12c9d1928ba7bec128dc985d5375791","tid":1907280,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:02:27.000Z","msg":"人民幣嘅力量，似乎影響世界好深<br />\n反而𠵱家有啲膽心美國喺世界嘅影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}